  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractMitabColumnFeeder, DefaultExtendedMitabColumnFeeder, DefaultMitabColumnFeeder, ExtendedMitabInteractionEvidenceFeeder, ExtendedMitabModelledInteractionFeeder, MitabInteractionEvidenceFeeder, MitabModelledInteractionFeeder

    public interface MitabColumnFeeder<T extends BinaryInteraction,P extends Participant>
    A MITAB 2.5 column feeder will write the content of MITAB 2.5 columns
